* Dinobot continued to swipe at Scourge, the Predacon would have to get 
tired of blocking his strikes sooner or later. But then he decided to speed 
up the pace of this little meeting, Dinobot began to strike faster and not 
just at Scourge's head and chest. He struck at his legs and arms, his 
shoulders and his neck. Finally he drew back with one hand and sent his claw 
towards Scourge's spark cavity, it was so fast that the air whistled as the 
claw cut through it.
Dinobot growled deeply as he sent his claw for a deathly collision towards 
his enemies spark, sooner or later he would have this bot's spark!
He had no time to let her know but he knew that Tavatron was only a few 
steps away, just in the reach of Scourge!
Dinobot roared as he targeted with his laser site and fired at Scourge's 
optic, he'd be to busy defending himself from his swipes to defend his optic 
from a sudden attack.
He didn't even want this tyrant near Tavatron, he was having trouble with 
him, he didn't want her to end up dealing with the same thing!*
